    <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
      <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
          <p xml:id="Aink425-kilavi">viṉaimuṟṟi mīḷum talaimakaṉ tērppākaṟkuc colliyatu.</p>
          <p xml:lang="en">The hero, who was returning having completed [his] work, spoke [this] to the charioteer.</p>
            </div>
        <div rend="parallel">
          <lg xml:id="Aink425">        
            <l>puṉpuṟap pēṭai cēva liṉpuṟa</l>
            <l>maṉṉa riyavari ṉiraṅkuṅ kāṉam</l>
            <l>vallai neṭuntēr kaṭavi</l>
            <l>ṉalla larunō yoḻittalemak keḷitē.</l>
          </lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">          
<l>Through the forest where the ruddy<note xml:lang="en" place="foot">I undestand <q xml:lang="ta-Latn"><hi rend="italic">puṉ puṟap</hi></q> as 'ruddy exterior'.</note> peahen, for the cock's enjoyment,</l>
<l>calls out, [sounding] like the king's musicians,</l>
<l>if you quickly drive the tall chariot,</l>
<l>it will be easy to cast off [her] unhappy difficult affliction.</l>    
</lg>     
        </div>
      </body>
    </text>
